Overview
========

**informan** is a man(1)-like info viewer.

Example
-------

.. figure:: doc/screenshot.svg

   “``informan du``” with less_ as the pager.

   .. _less:
      https://www.greenwoodsoftware.com/less/

Requirements
============

* stand-alone GNU Info

* Perl ≥ 5.10

* `File::Which <https://metacpan.org/dist/File-Which>`_

* `IPC::System::Simple <https://metacpan.org/dist/IPC-System-Simple>`_

